{
  "texts": [
    "Further tests with different settings for text summarization have shown that the summary generally works very well, but that too much world knowledge is added from the LLM training data.",
    "Figure 4 shows an example of automated summarization.",
    "The starting point of the experimental study is a realistic scenario from military intelligence analysis.",
    "A total of 50 source texts was collected from publicly accessible news portals on the internet.",
    "The sources were stored in deepCOM and served as a text database."
  ]
}